item.name: Profile Config Storage API | config/stores/ | move to internal folder

request.description:
This looks like it's part of the Segmentation Service API b/c it's got data/core/ups
but, it doesn't actually appear in the Swagger section of that API page
perhaps it's somewhere else. Move this to a seperate folder for internal API calls.------------------------- It's not in the public api docs.
